These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, country, folk
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, japanese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skateboarding, snowboarding
There 3 different types of food: potato, zucchini, pomegranate
1. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the american##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
6. the japanese is the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2       |     3      |
| Music-Genre           | punk        | country     | folk    |
| Nationality   | japanese      | american     | indonesian |
| Sport         | skateboarding | snowboarding | handball   |
| Food     | pomegranate        | zucchini      | potato        |

