.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, amber, coral
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, baccarat, aristoff
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, train
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person who likes coral is between the baccarat-smoker and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the aristoff-smoker is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person driving the train##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes yellow##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage    | coffee    | iced-tea | almond-milk |
| Color       | amber   | coral  | yellow  |
| Cigar         | baccarat      | game     | aristoff    |
| Transport   | motorbike | train    | ship        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, designer, manager
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, spanish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bluemaster, bongani
1. the designer is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the analyst is on the far left or far right##3
3. the bluemaster-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the manager##2
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the analyst##3
5. the italian is the italian##1
6. the havana-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Beverage         | lemonade | sprite | hot-chocolate |
| Job           | manager     | designer    | analyst |
| Nationality   | french      | spanish     | italian |
| Cigar           | bongani         | bluemaster      | havana    |

