.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
3 different games are played: whist, go, domino
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, western, romance
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, writing
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, canadian, nigerian
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person playing go is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching romance movies is between the nigerian and the person watching adventure movies##2
7. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Game      | go | whist       | domino   |
| Movie-Genre          | adventure   | romance   | western     |
| Hobby         | singing  | puzzles    | writing  |
| Nationality   | canadian | australian | nigerian |

