.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, cricket
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, pepper, radish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, indie
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, fuchsia, pink
1. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the right of the fan of classical##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person eating pepper and the person eating radish##2
6. the person who likes lilac is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the fan of indie##1
8. the person eating pepper is the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport      | skateboarding   | cricket    | weightlifting   |
| Food          | radish | eggplant  | pepper |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | classical | indie  |
| Color     | lilac | fuchsia   | pink  |

