.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, lemon, pomegranate
House: futuristic, tower, gothic-revival
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel
3 different games are played: snooker, go, domino
1. the person eating asparagus is the person playing snooker##1
2. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the person playing snooker##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
6. the person eating asparagus is the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching action movies is between the person playing domino and the tower house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| Food          | asparagus | lemon    | pomegranate  |
| House           | tower      | futuristic  | gothic-revival |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | action   | time-travel  |
| Game           | snooker      | go | domino        |

