.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, daffodil, rose
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, disaster, western
3 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, rugby, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
8. the owner of the cat is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Flower   | begonia         | rose      | daffodil   |
| Movie-Genre        | western | disaster          | scientific |
| Pet        | cat         | lizard        | pony       |
| Sport      | rugby       | skateboarding | golf       |

