.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, woodworking
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, teacher
City: boston, marseilles, new-york
House: townhouse, colonial, ranch-style
1. the teacher is the townhouse house##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the ranch-style house##1
6. the teacher is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Hobby       | woodworking | baking    | photography |
| Job         | fisherman   | paramedic | teacher     |
| City         | marseilles  | new-york     | boston        |
| House   | ranch-style       | colonial   | townhouse         |

