House: art-deco, cape-cod, victorian
1. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the cape-cod house is the cape-cod house##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person eating kale##1
5. the fan of classical is the person who likes brown##1
6. the person who likes red is between the art-deco house and the cape-cod house##2
7. the fan of d&b is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
