The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, animation
1. the owner of the lizard is between the person drinking milk and the owner of the ferret##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
