3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, cain, dunhill
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, sports
There are 3 different nationalities: british, german, nigerian
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the german##3
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the game-smoker##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
6. the british is on the far right##1
7. the person watching drama movies is between the game-smoker and the cain-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
