.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, dutch, polish
There 3 different types of food: apple, kiwi, tomato
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, puzzles
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, water-polo
1. the person eating tomato is between the person eating apple and the person eating kiwi##2
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the dutch is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating tomato is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is sailing##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the malaysian##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |      3      |
| Nationality   | dutch | polish    | malaysian |
| Food       | kiwi          | tomato     | apple       |
| Hobby      | puzzles       | card-games | board-games |
| Sport        | lacrosse          | water-polo       | sailing        |

