There 3 different types of food: kiwi, grapefruit, apple
3 different pets are kept: cat, rat, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, handball
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating apple##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar   | blend     | baccarat   | bluemaster   |
| Food   | grapefruit   | apple | kiwi |
| Pet           | cat        | turtle    | rat       |
| Sport         | basketball | cycling   | handball  |

