.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-16::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, mirinda
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, singing, writing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, may, july
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | cola    | lemonade | mirinda  |
| Hobby         | singing | writing  | reading  |
| Birthday   | may | june     | july |
| Sport   | parkour   | tennis     | cricket     |

