.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-17::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, reading, sudoku
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, golf, badminton
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, rock, salsa
There are 3 different nationalities: french, russian, egyptian
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the french##1
2. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's sport is badminton##2
6. the fan of salsa is the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | reading      | sudoku     | collecting |
| Sport           | skiing | golf | badminton     |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | rock       | salsa      |
| Nationality           | french          | russian       | egyptian     |

