.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, siglo, bongani
City: london, venice, hannover
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the bike##2
2. the bongani-smoker is the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
5. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
6. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Cigar      | havana    | siglo        | bongani |
| City   | london | venice | hannover  |
| Sport         | handball  | biathlon     | surfing |
| Transport     | bike      | snowmobile   | ship    |

