.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-19::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, garlic, peach
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, german
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, mirinda
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, van
1. the person driving the van is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
3. the person drinking sprite is between the nigerian and the person eating garlic##2
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the left of the german##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
7. the person eating garlic is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | garlic       | peach     | cucumber   |
| Nationality         | chinese          | german    | nigerian       |
| Beverage       | mirinda | sprite | lemonade |
| Transport   | bus          | van       | skateboard |

